---
description: Global code conventions for games-hub
globs: ["**/*.ts", "**/*.tsx"]
---

- Use TypeScript for all files
- Game logic in `lib/games/` must be pure functions with immutable state
- Client components use `"use client"` directive
- Shared game UI uses `GameShell` wrapper for consistent header, nav, and centering
- Game config changes go in `lib/game-registry.ts`
- No `console.log` in production code
- Use CSS custom properties (design tokens) from `globals.css` for all colors and theming
- All layout and styling uses inline `style` attributes — no CSS framework classes
- Extract shared style objects as top-level `React.CSSProperties` constants when reused
- JSDoc comments on all exported functions and module-level descriptions
